title: Anth
subTitle: Kali, the son of a gangster, rapes and kills Pooja, and frames her fiance, who is killed in custody, for the crime. As a result, her brother, Vijay, vows revenge against Kali.

title: Aakhri Adalat
subTitle: An honest police officer decides to take the law into his own hands when he loses his job, and the thugs he caught get released due to some technicality.

title: Aladin
subTitle: Aladin, an orphan tormented by bullies, discovers a magic lamp that grants him incredible powers. Later, with the help of a genie, he embarks on thrilling adventures to defeat the evil Ringmaster.

title: Dillagi
subTitle: Ranvir and Rajvir, two inseparable brothers, support each other through thick and thin. However, they find themselves in a dilemma when both of them fall in love with the same woman.

title: Hera Pheri
subTitle: Vijay and Ajay make a living by stealing money from people. Their friendship is affected when Vijay discovers that Ajay's father may have been his father's killer.

title: Devdas
subTitle: After his wealthy family prohibits him from marrying the woman he is in love with, Devdas's life spirals downward as he takes up alcohol and a life of vice to alleviate the pain.

title: Yeshwant
subTitle: Yeshwant, an honest police inspector, is framed and arrested for a murder. However, after being released from prison, he learns that his wife is having an affair.

title: Khuda Gawah
subTitle: Badshah Khan travels to India to behead the man who killed Benazir's father and win her hand in marriage. He succeeds in his mission but is caught by Ranveer Singh, a jailor.

title: Hum
subTitle: A man is determined to kill a cruel businessman to get revenge for his father's death but is stopped by an inspector who is the mastermind behind the troubles.

title: Hum
subTitle: A man is determined to kill a cruel businessman to get revenge for his father's death but is stopped by an inspector who is the mastermind behind the troubles.

title: Ram Aur Shyam
subTitle: Ram escapes from his home when he learns that his abusive brother-in-law plans to kill him. Justice is meted out when Shyam, Ram's long-lost twin, accidentally takes his place.

title: Bal Hanuman Return Of The Demon
subTitle: Bal Hanuman and his friends join together to defeat the crocodile demon who has been brought to life in order to create havoc on Earth.

title: Sohni Mahiwal
subTitle: Mirza falls in love with Sohni, the daughter of a potter but their relationship is not accepted and he is thrown out of the village. Later, he starts meeting her disguised as a shepherd.

title: Salaakhen
subTitle: An honest schoolteacher commits suicide due to the actions of the family of a man he testified against. In retaliation, his son takes the law into his own hands and seeks revenge.

title: Aunty No. 1
subTitle: To help his friends, Gopi dresses up as their aunt to solve their problems. However, he gets into a hilarious situation where he must avoid two suitors trying to woo him.

title: Hum Aapke Dil Mein Rehte Hain
subTitle: Love begins with a marriage of convenience and stays with Megha and Vijay in the throes of separation. In a classic case of unfortunate timing, one realises it too soon, while the other is too late.

title: Sholay
subTitle: Jai and Veeru, two ex-convicts, are hired by Thakur Baldev Singh, a retired policeman, to help him nab Gabbar Singh, a notorious dacoit, who has spread havoc in the village of Ramgarh.

title: Ram Jaane
subTitle: Ram Jaane, an orphan, grows up to be a criminal. His social worker friend tries to reform him but Ram is keener to win over his childhood love, Bela, than turning over a new leaf.

title: Ram Jaane
subTitle: Ram Jaane, an orphan, grows up to be a criminal. His social worker friend tries to reform him but Ram is keener to win over his childhood love, Bela, than turning over a new leaf.

title: Naina
subTitle: After years of blindness caused by an accident, Naina gets a successful cornea transplant. However, she soon begins to see terrifying visions that prompt her to investigate the source of her sight.

title: Bal Hanuman 2
subTitle: Bal Hanuman harmlessly misuses his natural gift while fighting demons and lands in trouble. Soon enough, he approaches Lord Sun in order to gain control over his superpowers.

title: Bewaffa Se Waffa
subTitle: Rukhsar asks her best friend Nagma to marry her husband, Aslam, and mother a child for him when she is unable to do it herself. However, problems begin when Nagma's relatives cause discord among them.

title: Dilwale
subTitle: Despite the family rivalry, Raj and Meera fall in love other but a misunderstanding causes them to part ways. Years later, fate brings them together when their siblings fall for each other.

title: Jai Vikraanta
subTitle: When a poor, honest farmer from rural India is killed by a greedy landlord, his son, Vikraanta, takes a vow to avenge his murder.

title: Darr
subTitle: Swept up in a whirlwind of fear and romance, Kiran teeters on the edge of a mental and emotional precipice. While Sunil keeps holding on to her, Rahul spares no effort to drag her down with himself.

title: Bhagam Bhaag
subTitle: A drama troupe flies to London for a performance. However, things take a tragic turn when three members of their team are falsely accused of murder.

title: Tiger Zinda Hai
subTitle: RAW Agent Tiger joins forces with Zoya in order to rescue a group of nurses who are held hostage by a terrorist organisation.
